=== Hypothesis Tester: plex state-bind ownership (task-1781916305-11ec debug:reproduce) 2026-07-15 ===

HYPOTHESIS: host dir backing the rw state-dir bind mount carries RAW in-CT ownership
  (999:991) instead of idmap-shifted (100999:100991); under CT110 uid map 'u 0 100000 65536'
  raw ids fall outside [100000,165536) -> surface as 65534/nobody -> in-CT plex gets only
  'other' r-x on mode-0755 dirs -> cannot write -> PMS 'Read/write access is required' abort.

DESIGN: two probe dirs, SAME parent / dataset / bind mount / mode 0755 / same CT / same plex.
  SOLE VARIABLE = host-side ownership.  PRIMARY=.hyptest-shifted(100999:100991)
  ADVERSARIAL NEIGHBOR=.hyptest-raw(999:991, reproduces current broken state).
  Pass criterion: shifted -> in-CT plex:plex + write OK ; raw -> in-CT 65534 + write DENIED.

